Groove CountryWaltz

Bass Sequence -

Begin Walk
	Voice $_Bass_Voice
	Octave $_Bass_Octave
	Sequence W123 
	Articulate 75
	Volume mf
End

DefGroove CountryWaltzWalk  Countrywaltz with walking bass.

